  "stepText": "Then proceed to complete Tai Bwo Wannai Trio, killing Jogres for both the diary and Rag and Bone Man II along the way, catching a karambwan, exploring Cairn Isle and trapping a horned graahk also along the way and buying an opal (or better) machete from Safta Doc after for the diary. Don’t forget to claim the rewards from the three brothers, and buy a bronze spear (and cloth, clean it, for a scarecrow for Morytania easy diary and Falador medium diary, plant it on your next herb run. Leave it in whichever patch is second and plant sweetcorn for RFD/Sir Amik Varze).\n",
